init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You found it more appealing than any of the others, and you were very excited about it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a strange and wonderful experience.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Many of you wondered if it was actually real, but you knew that it had to be.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: reincarnate into a very tall man who was the president of a country and had billions of people worshiping him.
